<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Anzu Aero | Advanced Aerospace & Stealth R&D</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #f8fafc;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.8;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #091024 0%, #172a6c 50%, #0e6b72 100%);
            background-size: 30px 30px, 30px 30px, cover;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-position: center center;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 50px;
            background: rgba(9, 16, 36, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .logo span {
            color: #22d3ee;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #f8fafc;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 30px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        nav a:hover, nav a.active {
            color: #22d3ee;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #22d3ee;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1050px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .hero, .section {
            background: rgba(15, 25, 50, 0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 70px 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 span {
            color: #22d3ee;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #22d3ee;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-top: 0;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #22d3ee;
            color: #22d3ee;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .image-placeholder {
            width: 100%;
            height: 280px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #22d3ee;
            margin: 25px 0 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            background: rgba(9, 16, 36, 0.8);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header { flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; padding: 20px; }
            nav a { margin: 0 10px; }
            h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">ANZU <span>AERO</span></div>
        <nav>
            <a href="index.html" class="active">Home</a>
            <a href="contact.html">Contact & Partners</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>Advanced Aerospace <span>&amp; Stealth R&amp;D</span></h1>
            <p class="subtitle">An advanced R&D company specializing in aerospace technologies, aerodynamics, and dual-use innovations.</p>
            <div class="status-badge">Phase: Founding & Startup | Lead Researcher Initiated</div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>The "Anzu" Strategic Project</h2>
            <p>The Anzu project stands as our premier comprehensive scientific research initiative featuring advanced conceptual designs in modern aviation. The project integrates unique modern stealth innovations combining <strong>aerodynamic body power</strong> with <strong>radar cross-section (RCS) stealth</strong> (a two-in-one solution), utilizing lightweight composite materials optimized for exceptional performance and efficiency across both domains.</p>
            
            <div class="image-placeholder">
                [Placeholder: Anzu Project Conceptual Blueprint / Design Overview]
            </div>
            <p style="text-align: center; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.95rem;">Figure 1: Conceptual integration of aerodynamic body control and radar stealth.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Aerodynamics & Dual-Use Technologies</h2>
            <p>Alongside the Anzu project, our research portfolio includes advanced studies in <strong>aerodynamics</strong>, fluid/gas flow analysis, and high-performance dual-use engineering applications designed to meet rigorous civilian and military requirements.</p>
            
            <div class="image-placeholder">
                [Placeholder: CFD Simulation Results or Composite Material Analysis]
            </div>
            <p style="text-align: center; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.95rem;">Figure 2: Drag analysis and aerodynamic efficiency studies.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Anzu Aero. All rights reserved by Lead Researcher Ahmed.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
